In the final installment of the Resident Evil series, 
Milla Jovovich returns as zombie-killing soldier 
Alice, who's left to roam the ruins of Las Vegas 
with a small band of survivors when a string of viral 
outbreaks nearly wipes out humankind. Alice has 
always been obsessed with bringing down the Umbrella 
Corp. but now must battle the undead -- and her 
extinction. Oded Fehr, Mike Epps, Ali Larter and 
rhythm-and-blues singer Ashanti also star.
